It's 25 minutes,
half hour give or take,

272
00:15:25,974 --> 00:15:28,107
from Tenafly
depending on the traffic.

273
00:15:28,141 --> 00:15:31,744
I always think I'm gonna
go to museums and stuff.

274
00:15:31,779 --> 00:15:34,046
And there's some good ones.
You've probably seen them.

275
00:15:34,081 --> 00:15:37,149
But I always end up at Saks.

276
00:15:37,184 --> 00:15:39,251
And I come home

277
00:15:39,286 --> 00:15:42,121
and Herb always says
the same thing.

278
00:15:42,155 --> 00:15:45,123
How much damage
did you do, Peaches?

279
00:15:46,960 --> 00:15:48,794
We always do some shopping.

280
00:15:48,828 --> 00:15:50,562
My daughter is very generous.

281
00:15:50,597 --> 00:15:53,599
She even invited me along
to this wonderful evening.

282
00:15:57,670 --> 00:15:59,436
You get a hold of Silver Bells?

283
00:15:59,471 --> 00:16:02,573
No. That doesn't mean
he's not coming.

284
00:16:04,175 --> 00:16:05,776
I'm pretty much done waiting.

285
00:16:05,811 --> 00:16:07,712
Perhaps we should go.

286
00:16:07,746 --> 00:16:09,346
What?

287
00:16:09,381 --> 00:16:12,984
No, I think
we're gonna order now.

288
00:16:13,018 --> 00:16:15,852
Herb gets very peckish.

289
00:16:15,887 --> 00:16:17,854
I skipped lunch.

290
00:16:28,698 --> 00:16:30,933
Can I help you, Bert?

291
00:16:30,967 --> 00:16:32,835
You've already done
all you can do.

292
00:16:32,869 --> 00:16:34,537
Snapped this place into shape,

293
00:16:34,571 --> 00:16:37,306
expanded our business
while keeping it lean.

294
00:16:37,341 --> 00:16:40,409
Pending due diligence,
we're done...

295
00:16:40,443 --> 00:16:43,512
at $11 a share.

296
00:16:43,547 --> 00:16:44,980
Really?

297
00:16:45,015 --> 00:16:47,650
