You're right, Mother. They
must have been adorable.

318
00:17:46,706 --> 00:17:49,741
There's one yellow
and one brown

319
00:17:49,775 --> 00:17:51,810
and then three sort of mixed.

320
00:17:51,844 --> 00:17:54,779
Each one at its own nipple.

321
00:17:56,015 --> 00:17:57,448
I love puppies.

322
00:17:57,483 --> 00:17:59,016
Not the way she does.

